  "url": "https://www.nps.gov/grca/learn/kidsyouth/junior-ranger.htm",
  "title": "Be a Junior Ranger - Grand Canyon National Park (U.S. National Park Service)",
  "html": "<body class=\"ParkSite\"><span aria-label=\"Top of page\" id=\"__topdoc__\" role=\"navigation\"></span>\n\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div id=\"beforeSkipLinks\" tabindex=\"-1\"></div>\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"GlobalHeader usaGlobalHeader\" role=\"banner\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"exitModalLabel\" class=\"modal refreshableModal\" id=\"myModal\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h2 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"exitModalLabel\">Exiting nps.gov</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"></div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Schedule\" id=\"cs_control_481716\"><div id=\"CS_Element_BannerContainer\" title=\"\"><div class=\"cs_GridRow\" id=\"gridRow_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_GridColumn\" id=\"gridCol_1_1_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_830326\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_1939782_830326\">\n\n</div></div><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_481855\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_1939782_481855\"> </div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"Park-header\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"pull-left\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div aria-label=\"Alerts Notification\" class=\"AlertsNotification\" data-site-code=\"grca\" id=\"AlertsNotification\" role=\"dialog\">\n<div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"AlertsNotification__Status visually-hidden\" role=\"status\">Loading alerts</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Panel\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Header\">\n<h2 class=\"Tag\" id=\"AlertsNotificationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Be a Junior Ranger</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7138499\">\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_1939783\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_1939783\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-right\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/learn/kidsyouth/images/Junior-Ranger-Page.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"Ranger giving a child a badge\" src=\"/grca/learn/kidsyouth/images/Junior-Ranger-Page.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"Junior Ranger Page\"/>\n</picture>\n<figcaption><p class=\"figcredit\">NPS Photo</p></figcaption>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<h2>How can you become a Junior Ranger?</h2>\n<h3><strong>While Visiting the Park...</strong></h3>\n<p>Come to one of the park's visitor centers, backcountry ranger stations, or <a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/bookgift_srim.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1981865,bookgift_srim.htm,11006|\">Grand Canyon Conservancy bookstore</a> to pick up a Grand Canyon Junior Ranger Activity book. Specialized books are available for the North Rim, South Rim, and Canyon Explorers.<br/>\n<br/>\nThe <strong>Grand Canyon Junior Ranger</strong> books are designed with place-based activities to be completed on a visit to the park. If you are visiting the South Rim and need a screen reader accessible or fillable PDF version of the South Rim Junior Ranger book, <a href=\"/grca/learn/kidsyouth/upload/S-Rim-Jr-Ranger-booklet-full-508-fillable.pdf\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=7893594|\">please download that here</a>.</p>\n<h4><strong>You must be in the park in order to receive a badge, and we cannot mail Junior Ranger books or badges.</strong></h4>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7138500\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7138500\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2>How can you become a Virtual Junior Ranger?</h2>\n<p>If you are not able to visit Grand Canyon National Park, you can become a Virtual Junior Ranger at home! After completeing the activities for your age group, download your own Grand Canyon Junior Ranger Badge.</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7138218\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7138218\">\n<div class=\"Component FeatureGrid\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -medium\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/kidsyouth/online-junior-ranger-ages-4-7.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/kidsyouth/online-junior-ranger-ages-4-7.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A girl sits on the rim trail working on a booklet\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 640px, (min-width: 1200px) 550px, (min-width: 576px) 50vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/286F66BB-DE4E-0C80-61FDFCF282BAFF40.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/286F66BB-DE4E-0C80-61FDFCF282BAFF40.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/286F66BB-DE4E-0C80-61FDFCF282BAFF40.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Online Junior Ranger Activities Ages 4-7</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Become a Virtual Junior Ranger! Children ages 4-7 can find engaging activities and earn their Virtual Junior Ranger Badge.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -medium\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/kidsyouth/online-junior-ranger-ages-8-and-up.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/kidsyouth/online-junior-ranger-ages-8-and-up.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Two people sit by the Colorado River in the Grand Canyon working on a workbook\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 640px, (min-width: 1200px) 550px, (min-width: 576px) 50vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/28AB359E-E1EF-4DFD-E663A716E0E36551.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/28AB359E-E1EF-4DFD-E663A716E0E36551.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/28AB359E-E1EF-4DFD-E663A716E0E36551.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Online Junior Ranger Ages 8 and up</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Become a Virtual Junior Ranger! Ages 8 and up can learn more about Grand Canyon while working to earn a Virtual Junior Ranger Badge.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6848532\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6848532\">\n<div class=\"Component ListingGrid -large\">\n<div class=\"ListingGrid-header\">\n<h2 class=\"Tag\">Programs for Junior Rangers</h2>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"row\">\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/ranger-program.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'/grca/planyourvisit/ranger-program.htm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A park ranger points out fossils for a few kids.\" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/D6F95C59-1DD8-B71B-0B8606E1CC2BC1E5.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/D6F95C59-1DD8-B71B-0B8606E1CC2BC1E5.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nView Current Ranger Program Schedules\n<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-angle-right\"></i>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">Attend any of these programs to fulfill your Junior Ranger requirements.</p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/photosmultimedia/virtualtour.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'/grca/learn/photosmultimedia/virtualtour.htm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A group of park visitors listening to a ranger talk. The ranger is on the right and smiling.\" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/1F633A3C-1DD8-B71B-0B261C3FE60B9054.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/1F633A3C-1DD8-B71B-0B261C3FE60B9054.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nRanger Programs &amp; Virtual Tours\n<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-angle-right\"></i>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">Ranger programs in the park remain suspended, due to COVID-19. Visit the link to take a Grand Canyon Virtual Tour. 3/1/2021</p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/kidsyouth/jrrangerfamily.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'/grca/learn/kidsyouth/jrrangerfamily.htm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A row of hikers in bright colors follow each other down a narrow trail surrounded by vegetation.\" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/EFAB37A5-FAC6-4C79-4C3CDEAA538C1033.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/EFAB37A5-FAC6-4C79-4C3CDEAA538C1033.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nJunior Ranger Family Programs\n<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-angle-right\"></i>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">Join for a family-friendly program highlighting Junior Rangers. Park Rangers will emphasize youth education on these programs.</p>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7138221\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7138221\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<p><strong>There are a number of Junior Ranger activity books available online on a variety of topics related to national parks across the country. Whatever your interests, check out these cool Junior Ranger programs that you can do at home or in your local area.</strong><br/>\n<br/>\nYou can find Junior Night Sky Explorer, Junior Ranger Paleontologist, and more in these <a href=\"https://www.nps.gov/kids/junior-rangers.htm\" id=\"https://www.nps.gov/kids/junior-rangers.htm|\">online activity bookets</a> - <strong>There are 10 different booklets to choose from!</strong></p>\n</div></div>\n</td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-9 -->\n</div><!-- ColumnGrid row -->\n</div><!-- end container -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-content-size text-content-style\">\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Last updated: October 17, 2024</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n <!-- ParkFooter -->\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div><!-- end of <div main> -->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!-- the rest of the scripts are leftovers from before the centennial down and should be pared down where possible -->\n\n<link href=\"/common/commonspot/templates/assets/libs/colorbox/colorbox.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n\n<div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"outdated-browser\" role=\"dialog\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n</div>\n</body>",
